
Recipe: Grammy's meatloaf

Description: very similar to a recipe in the New York Times recipe collection

Ingredients

* sauce

1/2C tomato sauce
2T mustard
2T vinegar
2T brown sugar
1C water
* combine + mix well

1.5lb ground beef
1C breadcrumbs
1 medium onion, chopped
1.5t salt
.5C tomato sauce
1 egg, beaten
pepper

Instructions

bake at 350 for 1.5 hours
baste occasionally
